        "Sun, Apr 26 World Music: South Indian Classical",
        "Humanities & Religious Studies Mon. - Fri. 7:30 a.m. - 5 p.m., MND 5014",
        "Phone: (916) 278-6444 mndhub-office@csus.edu"
      ],
